title: The Good, the bad and the Cowboys
itunes:title: The Good, the bad and the Cowboys
description:
A room full of heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler – deliver a super-sized edition of the news, including a discussion on whether the Cowboys spent wisely on left tackle Tyron Smith. The guys then put their prediction hats on during another round of “What’s More Likely?”
